# The repo mixes the Rust rewrite with the upstream C#/JS reference tree. The
# image only needs the Cargo manifests, the crate sources, and the res/ data —
# so ignore everything, then re-include just those (keeps the build context tiny
# and avoids copying the reference server, .git, docs, node_modules, etc.).
*

!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!crates
!res
!Dockerfile

# Re-exclude build artifacts that the broad includes above would pull back in.
crates/frontend/dist
**/target
